      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/post1-rendertex/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi everyone! Hope you are all doing well.
Amidst one of my classmates&amp;rsquo;s projects, I had to create relatively simple UI VFXs on mouse presses and whatnot.
Curiously this has always been somewhat of a constraint due to Unity&amp;rsquo;s RT architecture, depending on the needs of your project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m going to break down a few quirks that may aid in your own projects, mostly if you&amp;rsquo;re just now getting started with these features!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
